                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9402" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1409</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1123 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">扭住成本“牛鼻子”，筑就效益好“丰”景——山西安装全生命周期视角下项目成本精益化管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Grasping the key points of cost management and enhancing enterprise efficiency--The Journey of Lean Project Cost Management for Shanxi Installation Group Co., Ltd. from a Full Lifecycle Perspective</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵晓铃，王涛，刘超，王宇豪，苗可雨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西省安装集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全生命周期；成本精益化管理；BIM5D</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">full life cycle；Lean Cost Management；BIM5D</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">矢志成为集设计咨询、投资建设、建筑施工、运营维保为一体的建筑全生命周期的“国内具竞争力的现代工程服务商”，这是山西省安装集团股份有限公司在新时代高质量发展的要求下对自身发展提出的新愿景，更是我国建筑行业企业在数字化转型与追求可持续发展的时代背景下，对企业管理迈向更高水平的缩影。本文主要描述了山西省安装集团股份有限公司，以建设工程项目质量为核心竞争力的同时，积极探索工程项目成本管理新模式，创造全新增长点。本案例中，以全生命周期理论、精益管理理论以及成本精益化理论为基础，从山西安装树立全生命周期视角进行项目成本管理，落脚到山西安装某100兆瓦EPC光伏工程项目成本管理问题，进一步聚焦该项目部如何从项目全生命周期视角，结合EPC项目特点，利用“BIM5D+挣值管理法”等手段，进行项目成本精益化管理。以帮助学生认识到项目全生命周期管理在工程项目管理中的意义，掌握项目成本精益化管理的要点，培养学生以数字化手段解决成本管理问题的思维能力，同时提升学生可持续发展意识以及社会责任意识。也为建筑行业企业的项目成本管理提供了新的思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Determined to become a &quot;domestic competitive modern engineering service provider&quot; integrating design consultation, investment and construction, building construction and operation maintenance, this is a new vision put forward by Shanxi Installation Group Co., Ltd. for its own development under the requirements of high-quality development in the new era, and it is also a microcosm of China&#39;s construction industry enterprises moving towards a higher level of enterprise management under the background of digital transformation and pursuit of sustainable development. This paper mainly describes that Shanxi Installation Group Co., Ltd., taking the quality of construction projects as its core competitiveness, actively explores a new model of project cost management and creates a new growth point. In this case, based on the life cycle theory, lean management theory and cost lean theory, the project cost management is carried out from the perspective of establishing a life cycle in Shanxi, and the cost management of a 100 MW EPC project in photovoltaic engineering is settled in Shanxi, further focusing on how the project department can carry out lean management of project cost from the perspective of project life cycle and combining the characteristics of EPC projects by means of &quot;BIM5D+ earned value management method&quot;. In order to help students realize the significance of project life cycle management in project management, master the key points of lean project cost management, cultivate students&#39; thinking ability to solve cost management problems by digital means, and at the same time enhance students&#39; awareness of sustainable development and social responsibility. It also provides a new idea for the project cost management of construction enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《成本管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全生命周期理论；成本精益化管理；精益数字化；BIM5D技术应用；挣值管理法应用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
